heaven is a playground is a 1991 film based on rick &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; 's book of the same name . it was written and directed by randall fried , and stars michael warren , d.b. sweeney , victor love , bo kimble , richard jordan and janet julian . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; himself has a cameo appearance in the movie . the film was released on october 4 , 1991 , by new line cinema .